  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://www.aeluma.com/#mainContent) [Skip to footer](https://www.aeluma.com/#footer)\n[ ![Aeluma, Inc.](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/files/theme/images/logo-sm.svg) ](https://www.aeluma.com/)\n  * [Home](https://www.aeluma.com/)\n  * [About](https://www.aeluma.com/about)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/about)\n    * [Management Team](https://www.aeluma.com/about/management-team)\n    * [Board of Directors](https://www.aeluma.com/about/board-of-directors)\n    * [Certification & Compliance](https://www.aeluma.com/about/certification-compliance)\n  * [Technology](https://www.aeluma.com/technology)\n  * [News](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media)\n    * [Press Releases](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/press-releases)\n    * [Blog](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/blog)\n    * [In The News](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/in-the-news)\n  * [Investors](https://www.aeluma.com/investors)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors)\n    * [Company Info](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information)\n    * [IR Calendar](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/ir-calendar)\n    * [Financial Info](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information)\n    * [Stock Data](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data)\n    * [SEC Filings](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings)\n    * [Governance](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance)\n  * [Careers](https://www.aeluma.com/careers)\n  * [Contact](https://www.aeluma.com/contact)\n\n\n# Aeluma, Inc.\n## Built to Disrupt. Built for the Future.\nAeluma is a transformative semiconductor company specializing in high-performance technology that scales. Applications include mobile, automotive, AI, defense & aerospace, communication, AR/VR and quantum computing.\n[About Aeluma](https://www.aeluma.com/about)\n![](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2457/20967/image.jpg)\n## Innovating at the Chip Level\nOur technology innovates semiconductor chips to enable broad adoption in a range of industries. We are breaking out of traditional manufacturing to expand the reach of our technology into consumer markets including mobile phones, AI, AR/VR, autonomous driving and more.\n[Explore Our Technology](https://www.aeluma.com/technology)\n![](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2457/21304/image.jpg)\n## Transforming Shortwave Infrared Sensing\nFeatured in Compound Semiconductor Magazine, our technology redefines short-wave infrared (SWIR) sensor manufacturing by integrating high-performance materials with large-diameter silicon wafers, enabling next-generation communication and sensing systems for diverse applications.\n[Read the Article](https://compoundsemiconductor.net/article/120720/Realising_high-performance_sensors_with_heterogeneous_integration \"Opens in a new window\")\n## Latest News\nMay 28, 2026\n###  Aeluma Sees Accelerated Timeline for Quantum Commercialization \n[Read Press Release](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/news-events/press-releases/detail/107/aeluma-sees-accelerated-timeline-for-quantum)\nMay 21, 2026\n##  [ Aeluma CEO Jonathan Klamkin to Receive Prestigious Indium Phosphide and Related Materials Award ](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/news-events/press-releases/detail/106/aeluma-ceo-jonathan-klamkin-to-receive-prestigious-indium)\nMay 13, 2026\n##  [ Aeluma Announces Third Quarter Fiscal 2026 Financial Results ](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/news-events/press-releases/detail/105/aeluma-announces-third-quarter-fiscal-2026-financial-results)\nMay 12, 2026\n##  [ Aeluma to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conferences ](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/news-events/press-releases/detail/104/aeluma-to-participate-in-upcoming-investor-conferences)\n  * [ ![Visit us on LinkedIn](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21216/icon/icon-linkedin.svg) ](https://www.linkedin.com/company/aeluma \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on X](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21317/icon/icon-x-twitter.svg) ](https://x.com/Aeluma_Inc \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on Instagram](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21316/icon/icon-instagram.svg) ](https://www.instagram.com/aeluma.inc/ \"Opens in a new window\")\n\n\n\u00a9[Aeluma, Inc.](https://www.aeluma.com/) All Rights Reserved. \n[Privacy Policy](https://www.aeluma.com/privacy-policy) [Disclaimer](https://www.aeluma.com/disclaimer) [Sitemap](https://www.aeluma.com/sitemap)\n",
