       </video>\n    </div>\n        <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <button class=\"video-pause-btn\" data-target=\"ir-banner-video\" aria-label=\"Pause Background Video\"></button>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-left\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"text left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"sr-only\">Aeluma, Inc.</h1>\n                                        <h2>Built to Disrupt. Built for the Future.</h2>\n                                        <p>Aeluma is a transformative semiconductor company specializing in high-performance technology that scales. Applications include mobile, automotive, AI, defense &amp; aerospace, communication, AR/VR and quantum computing.</p>                                        <div class=\"link-container\">\n                        <a href=\"/about\" class=\"btn\">About Aeluma</a>\n                    </div>\n                                    </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div><section class=\"module module-default-contained  flipped\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center flex-row-reverse\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <figure class=\"module-image top-border-gradient\">\n                    <img src=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2457/20967/image.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1570\" height=\"940\">\n                </figure>\n            </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"text\">\n                                    <h2>Innovating at the Chip Level</h2>\n                                                    <p>Our technology innovates semiconductor chips to enable broad adoption in a range of industries. We are breaking out of traditional manufacturing to expand the reach of our technology into consumer markets including mobile phones, AI, AR/VR, autonomous driving and more.</p>                                    <a href=\"/technology\" class=\"btn\">Explore Our Technology</a>\n                                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>              \n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"module module-default-contained \">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <figure class=\"module-image top-border-gradient\">\n                    <img src=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2457/21304/image.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                </figure>\n            </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"text\">\n                                    <h2>Transforming Shortwave Infrared Sensing</h2>\n                                                    <p>Featured in Compound Semiconductor Magazine, our technology redefines short-wave infrared (SWIR) sensor manufacturing by integrating high-performance materials with large-diameter silicon wafers, enabling next-generation communication and sensing systems for diverse applications.</p>                                    <a href=\"https://compoundsemiconductor.net/article/120720/Realising_high-performance_sensors_with_heterogeneous_integration\" class=\"btn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Opens in a new window\">Read the Article</a>\n                                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>              \n    </div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"module module-media-latest-news-list \">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"module-header\">\n            <div class=\"row justify-content-between align-items-center\">\n                <div class=\"col-md-8\">\n                    <div class=\"text\">\n                        <h2>Latest News</h2>\n                                            </div>\n                </div>\n                        </div>\n        </div>